OL,3,CHospitality bosses warn NICs changes
OL,4,C'regressive in impact' on lower earners
OL,6,FHospitality bosses have told Rachel
OL,7,FReeves her changes to National
OL,8,FInsurance are "regressive in their
OL,9,Fimpact on lower earners", it has been
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FSignatories to the letter organised by
OL,13,FUK Hospitality, and seen by The Sunday
OL,14,FTimes, have said that "some jobs on
OL,15,Fminimum wage will become unviable" as
OL,16,Fa result of the new threshold
OL,17,Fannounced at last week's Budget.
