OL,3,CHospitality bosses warn NICs changes
OL,4,C'regressive in impact' on lower earners
OL,6,FThe letter reads: "The changes to the
OL,7,FNICs threshold are not just
OL,8,Funsustainable for our business, they
OL,9,Fare regressive in their impact on
OL,10,Flower earners and will impact flexible
OL,11,Fworking practices which many older
OL,12,Fworkers and parents rely upon.
OL,13,FUnquestionably they will lead to
OL,14,Fbusiness closures and job losses
OL,15,Fwithin a year".
OL,17,FThere was also a warning that "some
OL,18,Fjobs on the minimum wage will become
OL,19,Funviable".
