OL,3,CHospitality bosses warn NICs changes
OL,4,C'regressive in impact' on lower earners
OL,6,FAmong the signatories to the letter
OL,7,Fwere bosses at Whitbread and Greene
OL,8,FKing, the Times said.
OL,10,FThey are the latest in a string of
OL,11,Fbusinesses to offer warnings about the
OL,12,Fimpact of the tax changes in last
OL,13,Fweek's Budget.
OL,15,FEarlier this week, the Asda chairman
OL,16,Fsuggested there will be rising prices
OL,17,Fas a result of the hit they are
OL,18,Fanticipating from the new rules.
