OL,3,CHospitality bosses warn NICs changes
OL,4,C'regressive in impact' on lower earners
OL,6,FChairman Lord Stuart Rose said the
OL,7,Fincrease in employer taxes is "a big
OL,8,Fburden for business to carry".
OL,10,FHe said the firm will do all it can
OL,11,Fnot to pass extra costs on to
OL,12,Fconsumers, but it is likely to result
OL,13,Fin rising costs at the supermarket in
OL,14,Fsome form.
OL,16,F"We are a very efficient industry, as
OL,17,Fretailers.
OL,19,F"We will do everything we can to
OL,20,Fmitigate this cost.
