OL,6,F"But of course, you can't deny it will
OL,7,Fprobably be inflationary to some
OL,8,Fdegree.
OL,10,F"We're just working through the
OL,11,Fdetails of that now... We're looking
OL,12,Fat the impact."
OL,14,FSainsbury's have also warned of a #140
OL,15,Fmillion hit, while Marks & Spencer
OL,16,Fsaid earlier in the week that it would
OL,17,Fmean #60 million in extra costs, which
OL,18,Fwill be pushed higher by an increase
OL,19,Fin the national living wage.
